Package: shinyTimer
Title: Customizable Timer for 'Shiny' Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Maciej", "Banas", email = "banasmaciek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a customizable timer widget for 'shiny' applications. Features 
    include countdown and count-up modes, setting different timer formats, pausing 
    and resetting. This timer widget can be particularly useful for creating 
    interactive and time-sensitive applications, tracking session times, setting 
    time limits for tasks or quizzes, and more.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
  shiny,
  htmltools
Suggests:
  R6,
  testthat (>= 3.0.0)
